## ðŸš€ Quick Deploy (5 Menit)

Untuk deployment cepat, ikuti langkah ini:

### Step 1: Setup Google Sheets (3 Menit)

1. **Buat Google Sheet** di [sheets.google.com](https://sheets.google.com)
   - Row 1 (header): `id`, `title`, `category`, `price`, `original_price`, `description`, `images`, `tags`, `link_shopee`, `link_whatsapp`, `badge`, `is_active`
   - Tambah minimal 1 produk untuk testing

2. **Copy Sheet ID** dari URL:
   ```
   https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/[COPY_INI_BAGIAN]/edit
   ```

3. **Buat Service Account** di [Google Cloud Console](https://console.cloud.google.com/):
   - APIs & Services â†’ Credentials â†’ Create Credentials â†’ Service Account
   - Download JSON key (SIMPAN!)

### Step 2: Environment Variables (1 Menit)

Buat file `.env.local` di project root:

```env
GOOGLE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_EMAIL=dari-file-json@project.iam.gserviceaccount.com
GOOGLE_PRIVATE_KEY="-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----\nCOPY_SELURU_PRIVATE_KEY_DARI_JSON\n-----END PRIVATE KEY-----\n"
GOOGLE_SHEET_ID=SHEET_ID_YANG_SUDAH_DICOPY
```

### Step 3: Push ke GitHub (1 Menit)

```bash
git add .
git commit -m "Deploy: MechVault marketplace"
git push origin main
```

### Step 4: Deploy ke Vercel (3 Menit)

1. Buka [vercel.com/new](https://vercel.com/new)
2. Klik **"Continue with GitHub"**
3. Pilih repo `mechvault`
4. Klik **"Deploy"**
5. Tunggu 1-2 menit
6. Copy **deployment URL** (format: `https://mechvault-xxxxx.vercel.app`)

### Step 5: Add Environment Variables di Vercel (3 Menit)

âš ï¸ **PENTING!** File `.env.local` TIDAK otomatis ter-deploy!

Di Vercel Dashboard:
1. Buka project â†’ Settings â†’ Environment Variables
2. Add **3 variables**:

**Variable 1:**
```
Name: GOOGLE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_EMAIL
Value: dari-file-json@project.iam.gserviceaccount.com
Environments: â˜‘ Production  â˜‘ Preview
```

**Variable 2:**
```
Name: GOOGLE_PRIVATE_KEY
Value: -----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----\nCOPY_DARI_JSON\n-----END PRIVATE KEY-----\n
Environments: â˜‘ Production  â˜‘ Preview
```

**Variable 3:**
```
Name: GOOGLE_SHEET_ID
Value: SHEET_ID_YANG_SUDAH_DICOPY
Environments: â˜‘ Production  â˜‘ Preview
```

3. Klik **"Redeploy"** untuk apply changes

### Step 6: Testing (2 Menit)

1. Buka deployment URL dari browser
2. Cek:
   - [ ] Homepage tampil
   - [ ] Produk featured tampil
   - [ ] Klik "Browse All Products" â†’ Pindah ke /market
   - [ ] Filter berfungsi
3. Buka `/admin/dashboard`
   - [ ] Statistik muncul
   - [ ] Charts berfungsi

âœ… **Done!** Website Anda sudah online!

## ðŸŽ¯ Langkah-Langkah Deployment Lengkap

### â­ï¸ Step 1: Setup Google Sheets (10-15 Menit)

#### Langkah 1.1: Buat Google Cloud Project
1. Buka [console.cloud.google.com](https://console.cloud.google.com/)
2. Klik "Select a Project" â†’ "New Project"
3. Beri nama: `MechVault-Production`
4. Klik "Create"

#### Langkah 1.2: Enable API
1. APIs & Services â†’ Library
2. Search: "Google Sheets API"
3. Klik "Enable"

#### Langkah 1.3: Buat Service Account
1. APIs & Services â†’ Credentials
2. Create Credentials â†’ Service Account
3. Name: `mechvault-sheets-access`
4. Role: Editor
5. Click "Create" â†’ "Done"

#### Langkah 1.4: Download Key
1. Pilih service account yang dibuat
2. Keys â†’ Add Key â†’ Create New Key
3. Key type: JSON
4. Click "Create"
5. **SIMPAN file JSON ini!**

#### Langkah 1.5: Buat & Share Sheet
1. Buka [sheets.google.com](https://sheets.google.com)
2. Buat sheet baru: `MechVault-Products`

4. Tambah 1 produk testing
5. **Copy Sheet ID** dari URL

#### Langkah 1.6: Share Sheet dengan Service Account
1. Klik "Share"
2. Masukkan `client_email` dari file JSON
3. Pilih "Editor"
4. Klik "Send"

- Paste langsung ke dalam tanda kutip di `.env.local`
- Jangan hapus atau ubah format!

## ðŸ”§ Troubleshooting

### Common Error: "No sheet found in the document"
- **Solusi:** 
  1. Sheet ID salah
  2. Sheet belum di-share dengan service account
  3. Service account email salah di `.env.local`

### Common Error: "Invalid grant"
- **Solusi:**
  1. Private key format salah
  2. Missing `\n` dalam key
  3. Key sudah kadaluarsa/expired

### Common Error: "Products not appearing"
- **Solusi:**
  1. Cek Vercel logs
  2. Pastikan `GOOGLE_PRIVATE_KEY` valid
  3. Re-deploy setelah env update
  4. Cek `is_active` column di Google Sheet

## ðŸ’¡ Tips Optimasi

1. **Google Sheets Quota Monitoring**
   - API limit: 50 requests/second
   - Gunakan ISR (sudah diimplementasi)
   - Monitor usage di Google Cloud Console

2. **Performance**
   - Optimize images sebelum upload
   - Lazy loading (sudah ada)
   - Code splitting (otomatis)
   - Minimalkan bundle size

3. **SEO**
   - Meta tags (perlu ditambahkan)
   - Sitemap.xml
   - Robots.txt
   - Structured data
